Warhead: Good. East patrol, follow me.

He makes his way out of the ship. Using his internal compass, he moves 
towards the east.

Warhead: Inferno, Rage, I want you to make an aerial recon first. 
There were reports about an armed group. Do not engage before I tell 
you. Drillbit, Nightshade, you two stay with me.
